Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On beishiramandaya sowaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:05.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On beishiramandaya sowaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:06.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On beishiramandaya sowaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On beishiramandaya sowaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Je to na tobě, Gohoudouji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:16.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ochraň slečinku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hned tam budu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:42.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bylo by lepší, kdyby sis, když ti bylo sedm, zvolila smrt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Škoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Budeš se moct jen dívat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Zabiješ ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nechápeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Myslím tím muže, který pro tebe zemře.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Zabiješ ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:16.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On beishiramandaya sowaka.
